  "texts": [
    "If additional input is needed, the client sends follow-up messages using the same task ID until the task reaches a terminal state (e.g., completed or failed).3) Other Protocols: In addition to MCP and A2A, several emerging communication protocols are designed for IoA systems.• ANP.",
    "The ANP protocol [46] defines a fully decentralized P2P architecture in which each agent holds a W3C DID [36] for mutual authentication and uses end-to-end encryption to secure all messages.",
    "It also supports dynamic protocol negotiation to enable flexible and efficient collaboration.",
    "The AGNTCY protocol [111] focuses on building an open and interoperable IoA infrastructure.",
    "Built atop the agent connect protocol [113], it provides a standard interface for agent invocation and specifies agent capabilities and communication patterns, facilitating standardized inter-agent collaboration."
  ],
